[Course_Description]
Networking can benefit you regardless of your career path, boost your business, and enhance your life in significant ways. But not everyone knows where to start, or how to do it right. Discover 21 easy ways to improve your networking skills. In this course, explore how to connect with online groups, use social media effectively, take advantage of clubs, and even create your own podcasts, groups, and events. From volunteering to attending a tradeshow, the powerful tips provided highlight opportunities you might have overlooked, and could be the keys you need to connect with the right people.